  Range: 50 ft.
  Duration: Instant
  Area of Effect: 90-degree arc
  Saving Throw: Save vs. Wand negates (if HD > %caster_level% or > HD 6)

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Blindness
@61010 = ~Wand of Blindness~
@61011 = ~This wand will flash, temporarily blinding its target. If a victim is blinded, <PRO_HESHE> receives a -4 penalty to <PRO_HISHER> attack rolls and Armor Class.

