@61017 = ~This wand will use 1 charge to identify an item, much like a scroll of Identify, in that to identify an item you right-click on that item. A menu will appear and from here you choose the "Scroll" option. The chance of identifying the item is 100%. The charge will identify the item's name, what it does, and if it is cursed.

