//Protection from Evil
@61022 = ~Wand of Protection from Evil~
@61023 = ~When activated, the wand creates a magical barrier around the recipient at a distance of one foot. The barrier moves with the recipient and has two major effects: First, the protected creature gets a +2 bonus to AC and saving throws against attacks made by evil or evilly enchanted creatures. Second, summoned demons cannot target the protected creature.

