//Larloch's Minor Drain
@61052 = ~Wand of Larloch's Minor Drain~
@61053 = ~When activated, a small amount of the life force is drained from the target and adds it to the wielder's own. The target creature suffers 4 damage, while the wielder gains 4 Hit Points. If the wielder goes over <PRO_HISHER> maximum Hit Point total with this spell, <PRO_HESHE> loses any extra Hit Points after 1 hour.

