@61501 = ~With activation, this wand releases the power of a prayerful blessing, raising the morale of friendly creatures by +1. Furthermore, it raises their attack and damage rolls by +1. The wielder determines a point (up to 40 ft. away) where the effect will occur, affecting all creatures in a 15-ft. radius centered on the point selected by the wielder (thus, affected creatures leaving the area are still subject to the effects; those entering the area after are not).

