//Know Alignment
@62010 = ~Wand of Know Alignment~
@62011 = ~Activating this wand enables the wielder to exactly read the aura of a creature. If the creature rolls a successful Saving Throw vs. Wand, the caster learns nothing about that particular creature from the casting. When a character is hit by this spell, he will glow red if evil, green if good, and white if neutral. Certain magical devices negate the power of the Know Alignment spell.

