 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Melf's Acid Arrow
@62014 = ~Wand of Melf's Acid Arrow~
@62015 = ~The wand creates a magical arrow that speeds to its target unerringly. The arrow has no attack or damage bonus, but inflicts 2d4 points of acid damage (there is no splash damage). For every 3 levels of the caster, the acid lasts for another round, unless somehow dispelled, inflicting another 2d4 points of damage each round. So at 3rd-5th level, the acid lasts 2 rounds, at 6th-8th level, the acid lasts for 3 rounds, and so on.

STATISTICS:
(Conjuration/Summoning)

