 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Strength
@62020 = ~Wand of Strength~
@62021 = ~Upon activation, the target's Strength is magically set to 18 and then adds a +50% bonus to exceptional strength in addition to this. The character receives any strength bonuses appropriate. For example, if a character has between 18/50 and 18/00 Strength, then <PRO_HISHER> Strength will just be set to 18/00. If a character has a Strength between 18/01 and 18/50, then <PRO_HISHER> Strength will become 18/50 + original percentage. If <PRO_HISHER> Strength is less than 18, then it will just become 18/50. However, this spell will actually lower a character's Strength if it is already 19 or more.

STATISTICS:
(Alteration)

