  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Web
@62022 = ~Wand of Web~
@62023 = ~With this wand, the wielder creates a many-layered mass of strong, sticky strands, similar to spider webs but much larger and tougher. Anyone in the area when the spell is cast must roll a Save vs. Wand every round. If failed, the creature is paralyzed for one round. If the Saving Throw is successful, then the creature can move normally.

