Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Ghoul Touch
@62026 = ~Wand of Ghoul Touch~
@62027 = ~When the wielder activates this wand, a green glow encompasses <PRO_HISHER> hand. If the wielder makes a successful melee attack against a creature (1d2 fist damage + Strength bonuses), the creature must make a Save vs. Wand or be paralyzed for 5 rounds.

