//Deafness
@62036 = ~Wand of Deafness~
@62037 = ~Upon activation, this wand causes the recipient to become totally unable to hear any sounds. The victim is allowed a Saving Throw vs. Wand to negate the effect. Deafened spellcasters have a 50% chance to miscast any spells. This deafness can be done away with by means of a Dispel Magic spell or a Cure Disease spell.

