//Aid
@62500 = ~Wand of Aid~
@62501 = ~After activation, this wand gives the recipient of this spell gains the benefits of a Bless spell (+1 to attack rolls and Saving Throws) and a special bonus of 1d8 additional Hit Points for the duration of the spell. The Aid spell enables the recipient to actually have more Hit Points than <PRO_HISHER> current maximum. The bonus Hit Points are lost first when the recipient takes damage and may not be regained by curative magic.

STATISTICS:
(Necromancy, Conjuration)

Charge abilities:
– Aid
  – +1 bonus to THAC0
  – +1 bonus to saving throws
  – +1d8 temporary maximum HP
  Range: Touch
  Duration: %duration%
  Area of Effect: 1 creature
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Barkskin
@62502 = ~Wand of Barkskin~
@62503 = ~Once activated, the target's skin becomes as tough as bark, increasing its base Armor Class to %magnitude%. In addition, Saving Throws vs. all attack forms except magic gain a +1 bonus. This spell can be placed on the wielder or on any other creature <PRO_HESHE> touches.

