//Silence, 15' Radius
@62518 = ~Wand of Silence, 15' Radius~
@62519 = ~Once activated, this wand causes complete silence to prevail in the affected area. All sound is stopped: Conversation is impossible and spells cannot be cast. Each creature in the area must make a Saving Throw vs. Wand with a -5 penalty; if the save is failed, then they are silenced for the duration of the spell. Note that this spell does not continue to affect the area after being cast; only those in the area at the time of the casting are affected by the silence.

