//Clairvoyance
@63000 = ~Wand of Clairvoyance~
@63001 = ~Once activated, this wand empowers the wizard to see in <PRO_HISHER> mind the geographical features and buildings of the region <PRO_HESHE> is currently exploring. It extends to a great range, but cannot reveal creatures or their movements. This spell does not function indoors or underground.

