@63025 = ~Upon activation, this wand generates a skull at the target area. The skull floats in the area until a creature comes within 8 ft. of it. When this happens, the skull is triggered and explodes damaging everyone within a 12-ft. radius. The damage inflicted is equal to %magnitude%d6, or half with a successful Saving Throw vs. Wand. When casting this spell, it is wise to set it far away from the party lest they set it off accidentally.

