//Vampiric Touch
@63026 = ~Wand of Vampiric Touch~
@63027 = ~Once activated, this wand drains the target who loses %magnitude%d6 Hit Points; these Hit Points are added to the wielder's current Hit Points, with any Hit Points over the wielder's normal maximum treated as temporary additional Hit Points. The temporary Hit Points last for 1 hour.

