//Wraithform
@63028 = ~Wand of Wraithform~
@63029 = ~Once activated, the wielder and all of <PRO_HISHER> gear become insubstantial. The wielder is subject only to magical or special attacks, including those by weapons of +1 or better enchantment, or by creatures otherwise able to affect those struck only by magical weapons. The wielder also gains 25% resistance to magic damage. While in wraithform, the wielder cannot cast either arcane or divine spells.

