@63043 = ~Upon activation, this wand will cancel all Illusion/Phantasm spells of 3rd level and lower in the area. Spells that are affected by this are Reflected Image, Invisibility, Mirror Image, and Non-Detection. It is important to note that the wielder can control just who this spell affects. Therefore, it will affect only enemies of the wielder. The area of effect is roughly a 15-ft. radius around the target. The target's Magic Resistance, if any, does not affect this spell.

