//Melf's Minute Meteors
@63046 = ~Wand of Melf's Minute Meteors~
@63047 = ~Upon activation, this wand creates %magnitude% small globes of fire which are held in the wielder's hands in place of <PRO_HISHER> usual weapons. The meteors can be hurled at targets up to 270 feet away and are treated as missiles with a +5 bonus to the attack rolls. Each meteor bursts into a 1-ft. diameter sphere upon impact, inflicting 1d4+3 points of damage plus an additional 3 points of fire damage to any creature struck. The wielder may hurl up to five missiles per round.

