– Call Lightning
  – Lightning storm in area
  – Hits target and other enemies
  Damage: %magnitude%d8 points of electrical damage
  Range: 80 ft.
  Duration: %duration%
  Area of Effect: 360-ft. radius
  Saving Throw: Save vs. Wand for half damage

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Glyph of Warding
@63516 = ~Wand of Glyph of Warding~
@63517 = ~Upon activating this wand, the wielder weaves a tracery of faintly glowing lines in a warding sigil. This incription prevents unauthorized or hostile creatures from passing, entering, or opening. It can be used to guard a small bridge, to ward an entry, or as a trap on a chest or box. Any creature violating the warded area is subject to the magic it stores, although a successful Saving Throw vs. Wand enables the creature to escape the effects of the glyph. When the glyph is activated, it deals %magnitude%d4 points of electrical damage.

STATISTICS:
(Abjuration, Evocation)

Charge abilities:
– Glyph of Warding
  – Magical electrical trap
  Damage: %magnitude%d4 points of electrical damage
  Range: 60 ft.
  Duration: Permanent until discharged
  Area of Effect: 12-ft. radius
  Saving Throw: Save vs. Wand negates

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Hold Animal
@63518 = ~Wand of Hold Animal~
@63519 = ~This wand, when activated, holds animals rigidly immobile and in place. Only normal- and giant-sized animals are affected by this spell; monsters such as wyverns, ankhegs, and carrion crawlers do not count as animals. The effect is centered on the victim selected by the wielder; every enemy within 4 ft. of the target is also affected. Those who succeed on their Saving Throws are totally unaffected by the spell. Held creatures cannot move or speak, but they remain aware of events around them and can use abilities not requiring motion or speech. Being held does not prevent the worsening of the subjects' condition due to wounds, disease, or poison.

STATISTICS:
(Enchantment/Charm)

Charge abilities:
– Hold Animal
  – Holds animals in place
  Range: 35 ft.
  Duration: %duration%
  Area of Effect: 1 creature and any enemies within 4 ft.
  Saving Throw: Save vs. Wand negates

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Remove Curse
@63522 = ~Wand of Remove Curse~
@63523 = ~Once activated, this wand is able to remove a curse on a person. Certain special curses may not be countered by this spell, or may be countered only by a caster of a certain level or higher.

Note that the Remove Curse spell does not remove the curse from a cursed shield, weapon, or suit of armor, although the spell typically enables the person afflicted with any such cursed item to get rid of it.

STATISTICS:
(Abjuration)

Charge abilities:
– Remove Curse
  – Removes a curse affecting target, dispelling its effects
