  – Allows target to remove a cursed object
  Range: Touch
  Duration: Instant
  Area of Effect: 1 creature
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Remove Paralysis
@63526 = ~Wand of Remove Paralysis~
@63527 = ~Upon activation, this wand can free all allied creatures within the area from the effects of any paralyzation or related magic (such as a ghoul's touch or a Hold spell).

