 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Invisibility Purge
@63528 = ~Wand of Invisibility Purge~
@63529 = ~Once activated, this wand dispels invisibility from any enemy creatures within the area of effect. This includes creatures under the effects of Improved Invisibility, Shadow Door, Invisibility, Mislead, and so on.

