//Miscast Magic
@63530 = ~Wand of Miscast Magic~
@63531 = ~This wand will afflict the target with miscast magic. Any spellcasting creature that is affected by this spell has its casting ability severely disabled. When the creature attempts to cast a spell, it suffers an 80% chance of failure. Creatures can save vs. Wand to avoid the effect, but do so with a -2 penalty.

