  Saving Throw: Save vs. Wand (-2 penalty) negates

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Rigid Thinking
@63532 = ~Wand of Rigid Thinking~
@63533 = ~Once triggered, the target must make a Saving Throw vs. Wand or come under its effects. When under the effects of the Rigid Thinking spell, the victim will randomly wander, attack the nearest person, or stand confused.

