//256^2 :)
//Holy Smite
@63536 = ~Wand of Holy Smite~
@63537 = ~Once activated, this wand calls upon energy from the Positive Energy Plane in order to open a channel between it and the targets. The result is that any evil creatures within the spell's area of effect take %magnitude%d4 points of magic damage, or half damage upon a successful Saving Throw vs. Spell. If the victims fail their Saving Throw, they are also blinded for 1 round.

