//Spiritual Clarity
@63550 = ~Wand of Spiritual Clarity~
@63551 = ~This wand trengthens a creature's spiritual resolve and purges the creature's mind of negative influences. The spell removes the effects of fear, charm, confusion and feeblemind from a single creature.

