  Saving Throw: Save vs. Wand (-2 penalty) negates

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Dimension Door
@64002 = ~Wand of Dimension Door~
@64003 = ~This wand transports the wielder to any point within the current area. When the spell is cast, a dimensional portal opens up in front of the wielder, who immediately steps through it. Upon passing through the portal, the wielder finds <PRO_HIMHER>self at <PRO_HISHER> chosen destination.

