//Fireshield (Blue)
@64004 = ~Wand of Fireshield (Blue)~
@64005 = ~Once activated, this wand will evoke a blue shield of ice flame. This shield not only grants the user 50% Cold Resistance, but also protects the wielder from attacks made within a 5-ft. radius around the wielder. An opponent that hits the caster with any weapons or spells within this radius suffers 1d8+2 cold damage.

