//Fireshield (Red)
@64036 = ~Wand of Fireshield (Red)~
@64037 = ~Upon activation, this wand protects the user from fire damage by surrounding the caster with a shield of flame. This shield does not only grant the user +50% Fire Resistance, it also protects <PRO_HIMHER> from attacks made from within a 5-ft. radius around <PRO_HIMHER>. An opponent that damages the wielder within this radius suffers 1d8+2 points of fire damage.

