@64040 = ~Wand of Secret Word~
@64041 = ~Once activated, this wand dispels one spell protection† of 8th level or lower. The target's Magic Resistance, if any, does not affect this spell.

†: Spells affected by this are Minor Spell Turning, Minor Globe of Invulnerability, Spell Immunity, Spell Deflection, Spell Turning, and Spell Shield.

