@64042 = ~Wand of Minor Sequencer~
@64043 = ~Once activated, this wand takes the magical energy of the wielder and stores two spells to activate them both at the same time from <PRO_HISHER> Special Ability button. Both spells must be of 2nd level or lower. To create a sequencer, the wielder must memorize the spells <PRO_HESHE> intends to store in it (a Sorcerer can store spells of any level for which <PRO_HESHE> still has spell slots). After casting Minor Sequencer, the player will be prompted to choose the sequenced spells from those <PRO_HESHE> has memorized.

A sequencer lasts until activated and, once used, releases its spells immediately (no casting time). The Special Ability icon also disappears until the next time a sequencer is formed. A character can possess only one Minor Sequencer at a time, and it may not be given to other characters.

